{"config":{"separator":"[\\s\\-_,:!=\\[\\]()\\\\\"`/]+|\\.(?!\\d)"},"items":[{"location":"","level":1,"title":"HOME","text":"","path":["HOME"],"tags":[]},{"location":"about/","level":1,"title":"About","text":"","path":["About"],"tags":[]},{"location":"about/#about","level":2,"title":"About","text":"<p>Hello,</p> <p>My name is Johan Borgström and I am a 3D generalist / technical artist. Petfactory was founded with the aim to fuse Design with Animation. When I code I prefer to do so with Python and VEX.</p> <p>I studied industrial design at Umeå Institute of Design which resulted in a BFA in industrial design. I spent the first year of my masters degree studying interaction design at Umeå Institute of Design. The second year I studied design at HDK-Valand Academy of Art and Design which resulted in a MFA in design.</p> <p>Feel free to contact me: johan[at]petfactory.se</p>","path":["About"],"tags":[]},{"location":"houdini/","level":1,"title":"Houdini","text":"","path":["Houdini"],"tags":[]},{"location":"houdini/#unreal","level":2,"title":"Unreal","text":"","path":["Houdini"],"tags":[]},{"location":"houdini/#sub-ue","level":3,"title":"SUb UE","text":"<p>Epic pathtracccccer</p>","path":["Houdini"],"tags":[]},{"location":"houdini/#houdini","level":2,"title":"Houdini","text":"<p>Vex is king!</p>","path":["Houdini"],"tags":[]},{"location":"markdown/","level":1,"title":"Markdown in 5min","text":"","path":["Markdown in 5min"],"tags":[]},{"location":"markdown/#headers","level":2,"title":"Headers","text":"<pre><code># H1 Header\n## H2 Header\n### H3 Header\n#### H4 Header\n##### H5 Header\n###### H6 Header\n</code></pre>","path":["Markdown in 5min"],"tags":[]},{"location":"markdown/#text-formatting","level":2,"title":"Text formatting","text":"<pre><code>**bold text**\n*italic text*\n***bold and italic***\n~~strikethrough~~\n`inline code`\n</code></pre>","path":["Markdown in 5min"],"tags":[]},{"location":"markdown/#links-and-images","level":2,"title":"Links and images","text":"